node.text:
Struggling with writer's block, a novelist finds inspiration when she meets a down-on-his-luck oddball who constantly changes personas and alter egos to cope with the past and avoid reality.

With: @ilizasheslinger @davidkoechner @cleopatracoleman @trezzo_ @nickthune #ad #therightonemovie

node.title: Watch “The Right One” now on iTunes and ON Demand 🙏🥰💖

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on August 30, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'phoenix. Childhood trauma is so deeply rooted in who we are and we don't even realize it. We don't even know why we do the things we do and feel what we feel until we backtrack and turn inward.'.

node.text: makes my head hurt thinking about it
